<section class="py-32 bg-secondary relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-8">
    <div
      class="relative rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-24 text-center text-white overflow-hidden glass-card"
    >
      <!-- Sophisticated Decoration -->
      <div
        class="absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-96 h-96 bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-40"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 w-96 h-96 bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-40"
      >
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Badge -->
        <div
          class="reveal inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 mb-10 rounded-full ultra-thin-border bg-white/5 text-accent font-bold text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase"
        >
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent animate-pulse"></span>
          Cupos Limitados
        </div>

        <h2
          class="reveal text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-display font-black mb-10 leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter uppercase mercury-text"
        >
          ¿Listo para saber dónde <span
            class="font-serif-elite italic lowercase">pierdes dinero?</span
          >
        </h2>

        <p
          class="reveal text-xl md:text-2xl text-zinc-500 mb-14 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light"
          style="transition-delay: 200ms;"
        >
          Auditoría técnica de 45 min. Si no encuentro mínimo $1,000 de
          desperdicio mensual, no seguimos.
        </p>

        <div
          class="reveal flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-8"
          style="transition-delay: 400ms;"
        >
          <a
            href="/contacto"
            class="cta-elite-glow group text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] px-14 py-7 rounded-full flex items-center gap-4"
          >
            <span>Agendar mi auditoría gratis</span>
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
              >arrow_outward</span
            >
          </a>
        </div>

        <p
          class="reveal mt-12 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/10 italic"
          style="transition-delay: 600ms;"
        >
          Solo acepto 10 auditorías al mes. Si el calendario está lleno, lista
          de espera.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
